*v0.3* (2011-08-04)

* Altered the loading scheme for the polyfill to ensure the grid layout is always triggered, even if the polyfill takes FOREVER to load.

*v0.2* (2011-07-26)

* Refactored extension file to ensure the Polyfill library is available is needed before attempting to execute a polyfill
* Added Opera support

*v0.1* (2011-07-24)

* Basic Grid Alignment working in the following modern browsers: Chrome, Firefox, Internet Explorer, & Safari (Opera still needs work)